{"tid":1797309,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【華為5G】意大利議會敦促政府考慮禁止中資作為5G設備供應商","createTime":"2019-12-25T10:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:10:59.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"edf287f16d955abc0bc78b0bdcbb18e031b19607","tid":1797309,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"【華為5G】意大利議會敦促政府考慮禁止中資作為5G設備供應商<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2526104/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA5G%E3%80%91%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BD%9C%E7%82%BA5G%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2526104%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA5G%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2595%25A6%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%2587%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2582%25BA5G%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%2582%2599%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2595%2586&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFNkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=127c4fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2526104/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA5G%E3%80%91%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E4%BD%9C%E7%82%BA5G%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%95%86</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意大利議會的情報和安全委員會敦促意大利政府，非常嚴肅地考慮禁止華為及其他中資公司作為意大利5G網絡設備供應商。<br />\n<br />\n情報和安全委員會於審查報告中表示，由於中國政府有權干預公司活動，因此對起用中資公司安裝及維護意大利5G網絡的擔憂，是有根據的。委員會還指出過去華為於意大利供應的設備中發現的安全漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n華為表示，願意與所有政府實體展開合作，將提供所有必要保證，以便讓運營商迅速部署5G，又指一直強調網絡安全討論應基於事實，要求針對該公司做出的指控應得到證明。目前，沒有任何證據支持這些指控。<br />\n<br />\n中興表示，完全遵守法律法規，包括意大利的法律法規，指安全是該公司的重中之重，歡迎對公司活動展開獨立審查。"},{"pid":"4831e229b75294d25b87f15f59b2e1832a05d55e","tid":1797309,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"幾時八國聯軍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51912192fe147cc5a52b8f9b8577daefb732f1ef","tid":1797309,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"唔敢再笑意粉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2c27df16a669eed96a074a5b67244faf59b247","tid":1797309,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2450e4783832ab88589015e9c70c23b8c3e69f0b","tid":1797309,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"估唔到最奶共嘅<br />\n最先反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反觀廢國、左膠法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e95adb7d7154c2b71dc1d562e6923eeccb541c","tid":1797309,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:02:24.000Z","msg":"有冇得聯署表達意見?"},{"pid":"468df914dc90fec00720b0fdc8110aece4b37766","tid":1797309,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"估唔到成日俾歐盟笑豬隊友既意粉最先反共<br />\n反觀其他歐洲國家<br />\n德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617472a581759a3955b42cb4b1c75835f3e52f16","tid":1797309,"uid":315761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"勁過德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n默克爾對唔對得住元首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/l